display="inline"><![CDATA[I\mathrel {\trianglelefteq } R]]></fr:tex> where <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[I]]></fr:tex> may or may not be a proper ideal, just so long as <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[I]]></fr:tex> is not a principal ideal).</fr:p>
 
   
